{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168997864","path":null,"data":{"id":1175,"title":"AIA:推出「智悠選」團體保險計劃2及停售通知","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1658210922536,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 一、</span></strong>新冠肺炎疫情持續，為各位同心協力、共度難關，友邦保險誠意於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2022年7月21日（保單申請日起）</strong></span>推出<strong><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">「智悠選」團體保險計劃2</span></strong>，在維持與「智悠選」團體保險計劃<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>相同保費</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">同時</span></span>，為香港中小企市場提供<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">靈活彈性</span></strong>，新增多項保障及<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">靈活福利安排（FSA）。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 產品特色如下：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>指定門診手術之福利獎賞：</strong></span>每病症<strong><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">HKD 600-HKD 2,000</span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>精神科治療：</strong></span>每保單年度<strong><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">HKD 30,000</span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>靈活福利安排（FSA）：</strong></span>選擇調低計劃換取靈活積分，實報實銷賠償<strong><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">身體檢查、疫苗接種、視力保障及牙科保健，及AIA個人保單保費及保費徽費</span></strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 二、<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">「智悠選」團體保障計劃即將停止銷售</span></strong>，已簽署的投保申請書及齊全的所需資料正本須於<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">2022年7月20日或之前</span></strong>遞交。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Memo Ref A2022184.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-07-19/d667d0515da345d79d2437bc11e797db.pdf","uploadTime":1658196160776,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"Flexi Choice 2-EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-07-19/2166371d3c3f46998722bf009d5dd808.pdf","uploadTime":1658196165312,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"Flexi Choice 2-TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-07-19/9607cf801bd34800bd640afb21d25311.pdf","uploadTime":1658196169399,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:FCGIP","AIA:FCGIP2"],"productNames":["智悠選團體保險計劃","智悠選團體保險計劃2"],"companyCodes":["AIA"],"companyNames":["友邦保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1658365412992,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}